Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標清除\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Target confirmed kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午好  內森·詹姆斯號  我是艦長\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Good afternoon Nathan James. This is the Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在世界之巔經歷了四個月的艱巨挑戰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}After four very challenging months at the top of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛通過了終極測試\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}we have just passed our final test,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很自豪地說你們完成的相當出色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I'm proud to say you did it with flying colors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問問國防部今天能否取消無線電靜默\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm asking the Pentagon if we can break radio silence today
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打打電話  發發郵件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and make calls and e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向你們所有人表示祝賀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bravo zulu to each and every one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.84,0:05:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,享受你們的勝利吧  因為我們要回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enjoy your success, 'cause we're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫度即將降至零下50度  叫他們從冰原回來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gonna drop to 50 below. Get them off the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  長官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.85,0:06:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯科特博士  快回來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Scott, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯科特博士  聽到了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Scott, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Please respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯科特博士  進來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Scott, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是在逗我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就要成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.48,0:06:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得確保隔離病毒沒有被污染\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need to make sure the isolate isn't contaminated. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要更多樣本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need more samples.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  蕾切爾  我們可以明天再來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's all right, Rachel. We can come back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女士  我們一直在試圖聯系你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ma'am, we've been trying to reach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮官想讓你回船上去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}C.O. wants you back on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告訴艦長我準備好了就會回去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You can tell the captain that I'll return when I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是邀請  女士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It wasn't an invitation, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就回去  艦長的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Right now. Captain's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著陸準備已完成  起落架放下鎖定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Landing check is complete. Gear down and locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:06:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20英尺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}20 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10英尺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}10 feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.99,0:07:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著陸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Wheels down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們抓緊時間  還能趕回去比賽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We haul ass from here, we can make it back for the series.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會真的以為那幫菜鳥還有贏的希望吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't really think the cubs are still in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是棒球聯賽里最弱的分區\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's the weakest division in baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們離開時打贏了六場比賽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were six games up when we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是六月的事  他們都是新人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah, that was June. And they're the cubs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢德勒艦長  你沒權利不讓我工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain Chandler, you had no right to pull me from my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我要去看看...  -好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- I'm gonna go check on the, uh... - yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們來這里是為了支持我工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Those men are here to support me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能派他們帶我回來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't send them to bring me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人是美國海軍的船員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Those men are sailors in the U.S. navy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-直接向我匯報  -等我弄完準備好就回來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- and report directly to me. - I say when I am done and ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作至關重要  我終于找到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My work is vital here, and I have finally found
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-一直在尋找的東西  -博士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- what I'm looking for! - Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先  謝謝你上船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}First of all, thanks for checking in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們離開諾福克后  你頭一次跟我說話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Think this is the first time you said more than three words
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超過三個詞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to me since we left Norfolk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.26,0:07:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我很抱歉沒請你喝茶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I am sorry that I haven't had you over for tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六月在維吉尼亞州那會兒你的態度還算迷人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know, your attitude was mildly charming back in June in Virginia 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在這里  零下五十度\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but up here, at 50 below,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個月來沒人提起過家人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when none of us have talked to our families in four months,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就沒那么迷人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}not so charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:07:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-實際上魅力并不是我的  -還說呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Yeah, well, charm wasn't exactly my pri-- - Still talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在  我覺得我不僅是位和藹可親的船主\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, I think I've been more than a gracious host --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,載你和你的助手到這里的島嶼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}taxied you and your assistant around the islands here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你能夠追逐你的鴨群們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so you could chase after your ducks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那是北極燕鷗  -你得收工了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Arctic terns. - You need to wrap it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的任務已經完成  就要返航了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our mission's done, and we'll be heading back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝茶的事先延期吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll take a rain check on the tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.53,0:08:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本佐  吃點水果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Benzo, eat some fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  鐘先生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come on, Mr. Chung.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們在北極待得最后一晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's our last night at the North Pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你有好些遠大的計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Look, I know you've got big plans,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你就沒有不看書的時候嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but don't you ever get your head out of that book?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:39.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹尼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Danny, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.87,0:08:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那樣的笑容會誘惑到我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know what that smile does to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.60,0:08:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情場如戰場\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All's fair in love and war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.00,0:08:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kara...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們很快就回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll be home soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在聽我說嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hello. Are you reading me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}請勿觸碰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我等不了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No, I cannot wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是蕾切爾·斯科特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is Dr. Rachel Scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就要跟國家安全顧問通話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I need to speak to the National Security Adviser right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白  我的任務被連累了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You don't understand. My mission is being compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要更多時間來采集樣本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I need more time to collect samples.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頻道信號不好  重復一遍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have a noisy channel. I repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.90,0:09:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務目標已實現  我們準備回家  完畢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mission objectives achieved. We are ready to come home. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  指揮官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's a negative, commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務已經拓展  完畢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The mission has been extended. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓展  為什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Extended? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持無線電靜默和當前位置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maintain radio silence and current position
