Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們肯定在融化的凍土上沾染了病毒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They pick up the virus from the melting permafrost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我們總算找到了海鳥的聚食區\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We finally found their feeding ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這么說你已經找到了治愈瘟疫的方法了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So you have what you need to stop this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只有回到實驗室進一步試驗才知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I won't know until we get it back to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒時間了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're running out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.69,0:17:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病毒在世界各地快速傳播\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The virus back home is moving quicker
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我們預想的要快得多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}than any of us could've imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.70,0:17:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How would you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們離開諾福克之后就一直無線電靜默\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've been radio silent since we left Norfolk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我自備有衛星電話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because I have my own sat phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.16,0:17:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在電磁靜默  沒人能知道我們的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were at emcon so no one would know our position!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.98,0:17:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們電磁靜默是保護我的任務\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We were at emcon to protect my mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}not yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是白宮下的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Orders came from the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把俄國人徑直引來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, you led the Russians right to us
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威脅了我全艦船員的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and endangered my entire crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須和國內的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was imperative that I stay in contact
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗室保持聯系  通知我們的進展\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with the labs back home to keep them informed of my progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.67,0:17:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你還不明白我們在說什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't think you understand what we're talking about here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請賜教\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Enlighten me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們離開諾福克的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}When we left Norfolk,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:17:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病毒還處于第二階段\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the virus was at phase two,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅在亞非兩洲小范圍傳播\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}limited to small clusters in Asia and Africa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們處于第六階段\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are now at phase six --
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全球蔓延\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}global pandemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.22,0:18:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界八成人口已經被感染\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}80% of the world's population is infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.19,0:18:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界都生病了  錢德勒艦長\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The world is sick, Captain Chandler...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.82,0:18:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奄奄一息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}very sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是告訴我全世界都不保了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you telling me the whole world is dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.36,0:18:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他們派兩個人來拯救世界嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and they send two people to save it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說服政府把我派來都花了好幾周\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It took weeks to convince the government to even send me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.39,0:18:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大多數同事覺得我瘋了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Most of my colleagues think that I'm insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瘋了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那箱子里的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that what's in that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是我們唯一的希望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}might be the only hope that we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長  美國總統要跟您視頻通話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain, we have the President of the United States on the vidcom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉讓你用這種方式發現\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm sorry you had to find out this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在能把樣本給我了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can I have my samples now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等待總統\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Stand by for the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  中校\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Morning, commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  你上次通話  我還是眾議院議長\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know. The last you heard, I was speaker of the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總統兩個月前去世了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The President died two months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨后一周副總統也走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the Vice President a week later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.26,0:19:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦政府剩余的人員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's left of the federal government
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.02,0:19:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都躲避在白宮地下六十米的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}is holed up 200 feet below the White House,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通訊也時好時壞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and communication is getting spotty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們現在想知道...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So we need to know now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.07,0:19:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯科特醫生找到自己做疫苗的東西了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}does Dr. Scott have what she needs to make a vaccine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她覺得她找到了  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She thinks so, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在向你發送坐標\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We are sending you the coordinates
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是座位于北卡羅來納沿岸的安全生物實驗室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to a secure bio-lab on the coast of North Carolina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.82,0:19:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人  我們剛被俄國人攻擊了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ma'am, we were just attacked by the Russians.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.32,0:19:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俄羅斯已經沒有正常運作的政府了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Russia no longer has a functioning government.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據我們所知\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}From what we're hearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一股分裂勢力在獨自運作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a breakaway force is operating on its own authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在確定所有消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're trying to ascertain all the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:20:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人  我們的家人  我們怎么能知道...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ma'am, our families -- how do we find out if...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望能告訴你  艦長\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wish I could tell you, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我國的大部分人口  包括軍隊  都在死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}most of our population, al-- with our armed forces, is dying or dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有同盟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have no allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有敵人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have no enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是滿世界病重絕望的人民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just a world of sick, desperate people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去幾個月  你的艦只幸運地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your ship was fortunate enough to be out of the hot zone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.76,0:20:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲過了高危地帶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}these past months.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果斯科特醫生有疫苗配方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If Dr. Scott has the makings of a cure,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們必須立刻趕回祖國\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}you have to come home...now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:35.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,供應鏈徹底斷裂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Supply chains are completely broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物短缺  醫院...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Food is in short supply. Hospitals --
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天朝政府對本國人民投下炸彈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}...Chinese government have detonated the bomb on its own people
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以阻止致命病毒傳播\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to stop the spread of the deadly virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.21,0:20:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著全世界近一半人口的死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}With possibly half the world's population dead or dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美國囤積疫苗的傳言甚囂塵上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}rumors that the U.S is hoarding a vaccine continue to swirl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}即時新聞  倫敦大火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市服務完全停滯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Urban services are completely overwhelmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大多數城市  全城電網癱瘓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In most cities, entire power grids are down,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通訊完全中斷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}making communication next to impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.91,0:20:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們紛紛質問  "政府在哪里"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}People are asking, "where is the government?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:21:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這病毒沒有治療方法  沒有預防疫苗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The virus has no treatment, no vaccine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-所以武器測試這回事  -都是借口\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- So this whole weapons test -- - It was all just a cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而電磁靜默\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And emcon alpha --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們不知道家里發生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}keep us in the dark about what was going on at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.39,0:21:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在法國沿岸有一個無人值守的加油停靠點\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's an unmanned refueling station off the coast of France.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.51,0:21:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們以傳動軸推進 就應該能趕到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If we operate at trail shaft, we should just make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎么知道他們的燃油夠我們橫跨大西洋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How do we know they have enough fuel to get us across the atlantic?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎么跟船員說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What do we tell the crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everything.
