Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.17,0:33:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得榮耀新生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}promised in the waters of baptism.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.95,0:33:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿門\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.79,0:34:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向左轉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Left face!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.08,0:34:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}疾控中心
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.86,0:34:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}設置序列號
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.16,0:34:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉槍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Present arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.45,0:34:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.29,0:34:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.20,0:34:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.73,0:34:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.15,0:34:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.76,0:34:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.43,0:34:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人都靠我了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}These people depend on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.58,0:34:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在處于一片未知領域\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm in uncharted territory here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.98,0:34:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We all are.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.04,0:34:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不一樣  你知道會發生這種事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not you. You saw this coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.09,0:34:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒想過會傳播這么快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I never thought it would spread so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.05,0:34:50.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我現在知道為什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But now I know why it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.67,0:34:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把我們從意大利人身上采集的血樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I compared the blood that we took from the Italian
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.74,0:34:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我們出發前采集的樣本進行了對照\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to some samples I took before we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.71,0:34:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病毒現在擁有一段超基因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The virus has an extra gene now,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.99,0:35:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只可能是被人為加入的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which could have only been added with human intervention.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.37,0:35:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病毒被武器化了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So it was weaponized.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.90,0:35:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.25,0:35:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是從某個實驗室泄漏的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Or maybe it escaped from a lab somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.55,0:35:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道如何消滅它了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I think I know how to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.82,0:35:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病毒的天性就是自我復制\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All the virus cares about is replicating.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.69,0:35:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改造過的病毒能夠不受約束的復制自身\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The engineered version lets it do that unchecked.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.86,0:35:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也就不再需要突變\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So it no longer needs to mutate,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.29,0:35:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此病毒很穩定  也就更容易被疫苗消滅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which makes it stable and easier to defeat with a vaccine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.48,0:35:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么之前沒有人這么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Then why hasn't anybody done that yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.76,0:35:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們都沒有原始樣本\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Because they didn't have the primordial sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.20,0:35:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.02,0:35:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦橋指揮室  請接艦長\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Bridge, commo, get me the Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.05,0:35:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長官  我們終于收到電傳指令了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, we finally got the comms up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.60,0:35:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This came through.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.15,0:35:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-來自總統的消息  -這已經是五天前的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- A message from POTUS. - This is five days old.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.66,0:35:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的長官  這是在無線電失靈的時候傳送的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir. It was transmitted while the radios were down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.47,0:36:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須確認這些命令  給我接五角大樓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need to confirm these orders. Get me the pentagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.24,0:36:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長官  我試過了  但是沒有回復\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, I've -- I've been trying, but there's no answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.27,0:36:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打給實驗室  給我接總統地下掩體\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'll try the lab. Get me the presidential bunker.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.25,0:36:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北卡羅來納不安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}North Carolina's not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.49,0:36:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總統希望我們改變路線去梅波特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}President wants us to change course for Mayport.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.38,0:36:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的杰克森鎮有一間實驗室應該很安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's a lab in Jacksonville that's supposed to be secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.65,0:36:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里和五角大樓都沒有回復\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's no answer there or the Pentagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.15,0:36:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長官  掩體也沒有回復\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, nothing from the bunker.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.48,0:36:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是我們的信號沒發出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe our signal's not getting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.60,0:36:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不我們檢查一下發送端\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We check the transmit side?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.81,0:36:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個問題  他們的電話能打通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not the problem. Their phones are ringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.67,0:36:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長官  我又收到一條消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir, I have another message coming through!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.72,0:36:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟總統那條消息同時傳輸的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was transmitted at the same time as POTUS'.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.49,0:36:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這文件看起來大得多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It looks like a much bigger file.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.80,0:36:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是個視頻文件  長官  -播放\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It's an mpeg, sir. - Play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.30,0:36:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湯姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.60,0:36:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在你父親的小屋里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're at your father's cabin.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.59,0:36:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說他有辦法通過五角大樓的關系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He thinks he has a way to get this message out
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.28,0:36:48.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這段視頻傳送出去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}through his contacts at the Pentagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.56,0:36:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你什么時候能夠看到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I have no idea when you might be seeing this
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.46,0:36:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是在哪里看到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.81,0:36:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都很健康\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're all healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.76,0:37:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們設法早早離開\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We managed to get out early
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.18,0:37:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經在這里待了幾個月了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and have been up here for a couple months already.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.11,0:37:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們跟你的兄弟姐妹失聯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We haven't heard anything from your brother or sister
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.42,0:37:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經有一陣子了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.03,0:37:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.98,0:37:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妹妹沒挺過來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My sister didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.41,0:37:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  親愛的  我們沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But, honey, we're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.67,0:37:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們真的沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.93,0:37:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真心希望你也沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And I really hope that you are, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.78,0:37:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.35,0:37:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come on out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.10,0:37:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是拍給爸爸的視頻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's a tape for dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.94,0:37:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來  過來問好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come on. Come. Come say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.03,0:37:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  你在哪兒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Daddy, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.08,0:37:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We miss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.18,0:37:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們愛你  爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We love you, daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.30,0:37:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以  就來找我們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Just get here if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.45,0:37:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們非常愛你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We love you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.43,0:37:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.20,0:37:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關掉吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Let's turn it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.94,0:38:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}美國海岸
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.11,0:38:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}梅波特海軍基地  佛羅里達
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.41,0:38:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道回家要干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know what we're going home to.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.88,0:38:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100英里范圍內沒有探測到輻射  長官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No radiation detected within a 100-mile radius, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.89,0:38:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使美國遭遇了核襲擊  那也不是這里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If America was nuked, it wasn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.61,0:38:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're home.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.39,0:39:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你要不惜一切研發疫苗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You said you have what it takes to make the vaccine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.37,0:39:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果情勢所迫的話  你能在船上研發嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If you had to, could you do it here on the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.38,0:39:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗室不是為此目的而建的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The lab wasn't built for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.06,0:39:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了收集數據\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's for collecting data.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.17,0:39:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果不得不那么做  你能嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But if you had to, could you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.58,0:39:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠征隊將進行提前部署\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The expeditionary team will forward deploy
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.60,0:39:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確保之后的部隊的安全\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and secure the area for the next group.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.03,0:39:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我們能夠找到補給\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hopefully we'll find support.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.07,0:39:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須做好萬全準備\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Got to be prepared for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.51,0:39:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人帶好自己的防化服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everyone carries their own biohazard suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.46,0:39:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人不動手我們絕不主動與人交戰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We do not engage unless we are engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.24,0:39:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們的人準備好  等待新的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Prepare your people and await further orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.02,0:39:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解散\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.43,0:39:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總統依然沒有回復\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's still no answer from POTUS
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.87,0:39:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅波特還有實驗室那邊都沒消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and nothing from Mayport or the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.60,0:39:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們連無線電調頻信號都收不到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We can't even get an F.M. radio signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.94,0:39:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電網一癱瘓  一切就都癱瘓了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}If the power grid's down, that means everything's down.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.18,0:39:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們到地面上去的話會知道更多信息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll know more when we get boots on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.30,0:40:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克  我們不回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Mike, we're not going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.62,0:40:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.79,0:40:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實驗室距海岸有200英里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The lab's 200 miles inland.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.24,0:40:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到新聞了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You saw the news footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.17,0:40:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迫不得已  我們殺也要殺出一條路來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll fight our way in there if we have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.82,0:40:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.65,0:40:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發電機可能就能用幾周\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Generators run out in a couple weeks,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.28,0:40:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定還會有平民想去搶奪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}maybe the civilian population tries to overrun it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.66,0:40:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變數太大了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's too many variables.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.15,0:40:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們怎么辦  就待在艦上嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, what do we do? We stay on the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.01,0:40:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-斯科特博士說這里一應俱全  -又是她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Dr. Scott says she has what she needs right here. - Dr. Scott.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.30,0:40:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有美國總統\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have standing orders
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.42,0:40:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接給我們下達的命令啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}from the president of the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.09,0:40:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是五天前了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}From five days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.34,0:40:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有上級指揮部門的情況下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}In the absence of a command structure,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.09,0:40:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣對我們的任務最有利我說了算\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I decide what's in the best interest of our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.57,0:40:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們這里的食物  最多能支撐一周吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And we have enough food here to last us what, a week?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.49,0:40:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃料又有多少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How much fuel?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.33,0:40:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要什么我們會找到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We'll find what we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.37,0:40:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我們會死在這里的  -不  不會的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- We'll die out there. - No. We will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.53,0:40:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湯姆  你這是好意  我心領了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tom, I appreciate what you're trying to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.06,0:40:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不會成功的  大家都想回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But it's not gonna work. People want to get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.51,0:40:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你說讓誰回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And who exactly gets to go home
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.98,0:40:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們艦上有216名人員  可只有80套隔離服\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when we have 80 biohazard suits for 216 people?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.07,0:40:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽簽決定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We draw lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.79,0:40:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能這樣做  邁克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't think like that, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.87,0:40:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣至少能給大家一個\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It'll at least give people a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.31,0:41:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家跟親人道別的機會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to get back to their families, to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.20,0:41:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓艦上任何人放棄希望的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not letting anybody on this ship give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.67,0:41:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你說了算的  你沒有生殺大權\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That's not your call. You don't get to play God.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.12,0:41:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我仍然是這艘戰艦的艦長\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm still the captain of this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.83,0:41:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務我已經說明了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, I've laid out our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.37,0:41:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你服從命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I expect you to fall in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.32,0:41:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦長到達艦橋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Captain's on the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.99,0:41:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左滿舵  全速前進\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Left full rudder. All engines ahead flank.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.56,0:41:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.83,0:41:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左滿舵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Left full rudder.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.70,0:41:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全速前進\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All engines ahead flank.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.98,0:41:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到  左滿舵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Aye, aye. Left full rudder.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.45,0:41:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全速前進\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}All engines ahead flank.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.55,0:41:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左滿舵  全速前進\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Left full rudder. All engines ahead flank, aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.12,0:42:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體人員注意  我是艦長\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This is the captain speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.58,0:42:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們與總部已經失去聯系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We have no contact with home,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.17,0:42:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有理由相信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I have good reason to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.62,0:42:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美國政府已經垮臺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}that the American government is no longer functioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.41,0:42:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們期望返回的國家已經不復存在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The country we all hoped we were coming back to no longer exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.59,0:42:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個月前我們作為\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We left these shores four months ago
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.64,0:42:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美國海軍  乘艦遠航\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}as members of the United States navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.01,0:42:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在我們不止如此\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But now we are more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.20,0:42:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們肩負著整個世界的命運\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now our duty is to the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.09,0:42:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本艦所承載的...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}On board this ship is the hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.09,0:42:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們的未來  我們的家人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for our futures, for our families,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.79,0:42:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有整個人類的希望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and for all of humanity,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.70,0:42:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們艦上的實驗室里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}because in that lab in our helo bay
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.10,0:42:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有結束這場瘟疫的解藥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}are the ingredients for a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.07,0:42:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而現在整個地球上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And this is the safest place on earth
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.07,0:42:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的科學家研制解藥最安全的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for our scientists to do their work --
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.72,0:43:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是216名美國海軍所保護的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}on a $3 billion piece of machinery
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.06,0:43:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘價值30億美元的戰艦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}protected by 216 sailors in the U.S. navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.62,0:43:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的任務很簡單\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Our mission now is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.80,0:43:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是竭盡全力在海面上生存下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We do whatever it takes to stay alive at sea
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.68,0:43:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到研制出解藥為止\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}until they find that cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.99,0:43:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關塔那摩灣那邊有一個\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's an unmanned food and fuel station
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.03,0:43:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無人食物燃料供給站\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}outside Guantanamo Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.28,0:43:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前我們的目的地就是那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}For the moment, that is our destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.00,0:43:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經失去了很多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We've lost so much already.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.88,0:43:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是本艦所有人員都英勇無畏能屈能伸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But this is the most courageous and resilient crew
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.64,0:43:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能與大家一起服役是我的榮幸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}with whom I have ever been privileged to serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.79,0:43:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們一定可以齊心協力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We will come through this together,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.05,0:43:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共同度過這個難關\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and we will prevail.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.30,0:43:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續前進\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Carry on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.49,0:43:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人員  立正\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Attention on deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.36,0:44:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格蘭德森上尉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lieutenant Granderson,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.37,0:44:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求向艦長敬禮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}permission to salute the Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.36,0:44:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求允許\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Permission granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.13,0:44:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉手敬禮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Hand salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.46,0:44:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}代號北極狐  我是海鷗
